{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio\/requirementsAA","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"text":"WCAG 2.1 requirement for AA level needs to have textual component matching 4.5:1 contrast ratio","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and non textual component matching 3:1 contrast ratio.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This is recommended for web projects.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio\/requirementsaa"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"requirementsAA"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OUDSFoundations18WCAG21Requirementsa","text":"WCAG21Requirements","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/WCAG21Requirements"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:15OUDSFoundations15OUDSWCAG21RatioV14requirementsAASb7textual_Sb10nonTextualtvp","roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","modules":[{"name":"Foundations"}],"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"requirementsAA","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OUDSFoundations18WCAG21Requirementsa","text":"WCAG21Requirements","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"title":"requirementsAA"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations","doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio"]]},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/OUDSWCAG21Ratio":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Some countries set up new laws so as to force companies to have a better accessibility of their digital services."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is for example the case for France with the "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"also named “RGAA”."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The WCAG specifications, for AA level, defines a contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This utility helps to define wether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"See for example "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"title":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/WCAG21Requirements":{"title":"WCAG21Requirements","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"typealias"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"WCAG21Requirements"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentatio